backend-UserMigrationDescription.message: Расшифрованная база данных паролей с паролями, папками, тегами и настройками. (Не включает пароли, переданные вам. Не работает при включенном E2E)
backend-UserMigrationDescription.description: Description text for the password export option in the user migration app. Exports won't include items shared with the user and the export only works if end-to-end encryption is disabled.

backend-ExportNotPossibleTitle.description: Title of the notification when a user requested an export of the passwords app data trough the user migration app, but we can't export his data because it's end-to-end encrypted

backend-ExportNotPossibleText.message: Поскольку у вас включено End-to-End шифрование, ваши пароли не могут быть добавлены в экспорт автоматически. В качестве альтернативы вы можете использовать функцию экспорта в приложении для экспорта данных.
backend-ExportNotPossibleText.description: Text of the notification when a user requested an export of the passwords app data trough the user migration app, but we can't export his data because it's end-to-end encrypted. The notification contains a link to the export feature in the app where the user can create an export manually.

settings-SettingsPasswordPrint.description: Label text in the settings for the option to show a print option for passwords

settings-SettingsPasswordPrintHelp.message: Показывает опцию печати пароля в меню и подробной информации
settings-SettingsPasswordPrintHelp.description: Help text in the settings for the option to show a print option for passwords in the list view and sidebar

frontend-PasswordActionPrint.description: Label of the print password action

frontend-FolderPickerLoading.description: Text of the loading animation while folders are being loaded

frontend-PasswordActionQrcode.description: Label of the action to show a qrcode for the password

frontend-PasswordTagAddExists.description: Notification text when the user adds a tag to a password that already has the tag

frontend-PasswordTagAddSuccess.description: Notification text when the a tag was successfully added to a password

frontend-PasswordTagAddFail.description: Notification text when the a tag could not be added to a password

settigns-ExpertSettingsLabel.description: Label of the option in the settings that shows additional settings intended for advanced users that allow more detailed control of how the app behaves

frontend-PasswordDetailsAdvancedView.description: Label of the option in the info tab of the password details sidebar that will show additional (technical) information that is useful for advanced users

frontend-PwDetailsEncryptionLabel.description: Label of the encryption method info in the password details sidebar

frontend-PwDetailsEncryptionTitleSSE.message: Этот пароль отправляется на сервер по защищенному HTTPS-соединению и шифруется там перед сохранением в базе данных.
frontend-PwDetailsEncryptionTitleSSE.description: Info text for the encryption method in the password details sidebar if a server-side encryption method is used. The password sent plain text over HTTPS, then encrypted on the server before it's stored

frontend-PwDetailsEncryptionTitleCSE.message: Этот пароль шифруется на вашем устройстве перед отправкой на сервер. Никто не сможет прочитать этот пароль, не зная вашего пароля шифрования.
frontend-PwDetailsEncryptionTitleCSE.description: Info text for the encryption method in the password details sidebar if a client side / end-to-end encryption method is used. The password is encrypted on the users device before it's sent to the server and can only be decrypted with the users encryption password

frontend-PasswordEncryptionCSE.description: Label for the client side / end-to-end encryption method

frontend-PasswordEncryptionSSE.description: Label for the server side encryption method
